{
  "id": "RAW_9e2ab3ee",
  "title": "面向企业的新用量分析与更新版支出控制功能",
  "url": "https://openai.com/index/chatgpt-enterprise-spend-controls",
  "date": "2026-06-19 01:00:00",
  "author": "OpenAI",
  "siteName": "OpenAI News",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"w-full\">\n   <div class=\"relative w-full\" style=\"--hero-aspect-ratio:16/9;--hero-aspect-ratio-mobile:3/4\">\n    <div class=\"w-full toc-visible:md:grid-cols-9 gap-x-(--grid-gap) [--grid-gap:8px] md:[--grid-gap:16px] lg:[--grid-gap:24px]\">\n     <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-span-8 toc-visible:@md:col-start-1\">\n      <div class=\"relative flex flex-col items-center text-center\">\n       <div class=\"mb-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center\">\n        <p class=\"text-meta text-primary-100\">\n         <br>\n        </p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"contents\">\n   <div class=\"w-full toc-visible:md:grid-cols-9 gap-x-(--grid-gap) [--grid-gap:8px] md:[--grid-gap:16px] lg:[--grid-gap:24px]\">\n    <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none not-first:mt-6\">\n     <p class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\"><span>As AI becomes part of everyday work, organizations need the ability to manage it with the same rigor they apply to any critical business investment. Companies need a clear view of usage, adoption, and spend so they can scale with confidence and understand where AI is creating value.</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none not-first:mt-6\">\n     <p class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\"><span>Today, we’re introducing credit usage analytics and updated spend controls for ChatGPT Enterprise. These capabilities help companies track credit usage, understand adoption patterns, and make more informed decisions about how AI is deployed across their organizations. With clearer visibility and more flexible controls, organizations can proactively manage costs, give teams the access they need, and keep AI investments focused on the work that matters most.</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full group not-first:mt-16 not-last:mb-16\">\n     <figure class=\"w-full toc-visible:md:grid-cols-9 gap-x-(--grid-gap) [--grid-gap:8px] md:[--grid-gap:16px] lg:[--grid-gap:24px]\">\n      <div class=\"col-span-full flex min-h-0 flex-col gap-6 toc-visible:@md:col-span-8 toc-visible:@md:col-start-1\">\n       <div class=\"flex min-h-0 w-full min-w-0 flex-col gap-6 @sm:flex-row items-center\">\n        <div class=\"w-full mx-auto ease-curve-c duration-medium transition-opacity max-w-container-desktop relative min-h-0\">\n         <div class=\"relative min-h-0 w-full\">\n          <div class=\"size-full\">\n           <div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-md aspect-auto size-full ease-curve-d duration-medium bg-transparent transition-[background]\">\n            <img alt=\"Billing tab and overall plan view in the global admin console\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"mx-auto\" style=\"color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1728px) 1728px, 100vw\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260618192256_Billing_tab_and_overall_plan_view_in_the_global_admin_console.png 640w, https://image.jido.dev/20260618192256_Billing_tab_and_overall_plan_view_in_the_global_admin_console.png 750w, https://image.jido.dev/20260618192256_Billing_tab_and_overall_plan_view_in_the_global_admin_console.png 828w, https://image.jido.dev/20260618192256_Billing_tab_and_overall_plan_view_in_the_global_admin_console.png 1080w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/943eea4f-abff-4476-028e-97a00f424800/public 1200w, https://image.jido.dev/20260618192256_Billing_tab_and_overall_plan_view_in_the_global_admin_console.png 1920w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cb2346eb-6cd6-4af8-4c31-f0ecf8a75800/public 2048w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/523156ab-dcf4-4aaa-e240-e525ab463a00/public 3840w\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/523156ab-dcf4-4aaa-e240-e525ab463a00/public\">\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <figcaption class=\"text-caption col-span-full flex w-full flex-col items-center gap-3\">\n        <div class=\"relative mt-3 w-full text-center\">\n         <div class=\"flex w-full items-end justify-between\">\n          <div class=\"grow\">\n           <div class=\"text-caption text-copy-secondary text-pretty\">\n            <div class=\"[&amp;&gt;p]:text-caption prose [&amp;&gt;p]:text-primary-100 my-0! max-w-none [&amp;&gt;p]:my-0\">\n             <p class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\"><i><span>Billing tab and overall plan view in the global admin console.</span></i></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </figcaption>\n      </div>\n     </figure>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none not-first:mt-16\">\n     <div class=\"w-full toc-visible:md:grid-cols-9 gap-x-(--grid-gap) [--grid-gap:8px] md:[--grid-gap:16px] lg:[--grid-gap:24px] toc-content-heading scroll-mt-header-h\" id=\"new-credit-usage-analytics-in-the-global-admin-console\">\n      <div class=\"full-grid-content:@md:col-span-full full-grid-content:@md:col-start-1 col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none\">\n       <h2 class=\"text-h3 scroll-mt-header-h\"><span>New credit usage analytics in the Global Admin Console</span></h2>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none not-first:mt-6\">\n     <p class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\"><span>The Global Admin Console brings ChatGPT and Codex credit usage into one view, so admins can see a more granular breakdown of credit consumption across users, products, and models—helping them understand where spend is coming from and how it maps to actual credit usage. This makes it easier to distinguish between increased usage driven by valuable work and usage patterns that may require closer review.</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none not-first:mt-6\">\n     <p class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\"><span>Now admins can:</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none not-first:mt-6\">\n     <ul class=\"mb-8 marker:text-inherit last:mb-0 in-[:where(ul,ol)]:mt-2 list-disc in-[:where(ul,ol)]:list-[circle] mx-3 ps-4\">\n      <li class=\"mb-2\"><span>Track usage and credit trends over time</span></li>\n      <li class=\"mb-2\"><span>Identify top users and emerging credit usage patterns</span></li>\n      <li class=\"mb-2\"><span>Break down credit spend across the workspace, including by user, product, and model</span></li>\n      <li class=\"mb-2\"><span>Access the same credit usage data through the unified Cost API for deeper analysis in their own systems</span></li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full group not-first:mt-16 not-last:mb-16\">\n     <figure class=\"w-full toc-visible:md:grid-cols-9 gap-x-(--grid-gap) [--grid-gap:8px] md:[--grid-gap:16px] lg:[--grid-gap:24px]\">\n      <div class=\"col-span-full flex min-h-0 flex-col gap-6 toc-visible:@md:col-span-8 toc-visible:@md:col-start-1\">\n       <div class=\"flex min-h-0 w-full min-w-0 flex-col gap-6 @sm:flex-row items-center\">\n        <div class=\"w-full mx-auto ease-curve-c duration-medium transition-opacity max-w-container-desktop relative min-h-0\">\n         <div class=\"relative min-h-0 w-full\">\n          <div class=\"size-full\">\n           <div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-md aspect-auto size-full bg-surface-loading\">\n            <img alt=\"Analytics overview showing ChatGPT and Codex usage and credit consumption\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"mx-auto\" style=\"color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1728px) 1728px, 100vw\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260618192256_Analytics_overview_showing_ChatGPT_and_Codex_usage_and_credit_consumption.png 640w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b2c300b3-deba-41c4-ba54-5473b2e6e400/public 750w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fbedc1ff-0443-4a42-7052-212b8ee59300/public 828w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ba7b825d-b10b-48c7-7012-5d273d599b00/public 1080w, https://image.jido.dev/20260618192256_Analytics_overview_showing_ChatGPT_and_Codex_usage_and_credit_consumption.png 1200w, https://image.jido.dev/20260618192256_Analytics_overview_showing_ChatGPT_and_Codex_usage_and_credit_consumption.png 1920w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/558739ad-6eb4-4480-90c9-e90a6e43cc00/public 2048w, https://image.jido.dev/20260618192256_Analytics_overview_showing_ChatGPT_and_Codex_usage_and_credit_consumption.png 3840w\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260618192256_Analytics_overview_showing_ChatGPT_and_Codex_usage_and_credit_consumption.png\">\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <figcaption class=\"text-caption col-span-full flex w-full flex-col items-center gap-3\">\n        <div class=\"relative mt-3 w-full text-center\">\n         <div class=\"flex w-full items-end justify-between\">\n          <div class=\"grow\">\n           <div class=\"text-caption text-copy-secondary text-pretty\">\n            <div class=\"[&amp;&gt;p]:text-caption prose [&amp;&gt;p]:text-primary-100 my-0! max-w-none [&amp;&gt;p]:my-0\">\n             <p class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\"><i><span>Analytics overview showing ChatGPT and Codex usage and credit consumption.</span></i></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </figcaption>\n      </div>\n     </figure>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full group not-first:mt-6 py-8\">\n     <section class=\"w-full toc-visible:md:grid-cols-9 gap-x-(--grid-gap) [--grid-gap:8px] md:[--grid-gap:16px] lg:[--grid-gap:24px]\">\n      <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-1\">\n       <div>\n        <div class=\"border-primary-12 bg-secondary-100 dark:border-primary-4 dark:bg-tertiary-100 relative rounded-md border shadow-[0_18px_60px_rgb(0_0_0/0.08)]\">\n         <div class=\"px-6 pb-8 pt-8\">\n          <div class=\"no-scrollbar relative scroll-smooth overflow-visible\">\n           <div class=\"sticky inset-s-0 top-0 w-full\">\n            <figure class=\"row-start-1 gap-5 self-start transition-opacity duration-250 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1)] opacity-100\">\n             <blockquote class=\"text-h5 text-primary-100 relative ms-[0.5em] font-medium tracking-tight text-pretty\">\n              <span class=\"absolute inset-s-[-0.5em] top-0\">“</span><span>Zipline’s engineering has been all-in on Codex since January, and in recent months the broader company has adopted it. We asked the team at OpenAI to build usage analytics to help find and train-up folks who haven’t adopted Codex, and for granular usage controls to keep spend predictable. These new tools are helping us faster scale productivity of our employees while keeping safeguards in place.</span>”\n             </blockquote>\n             <figcaption class=\"text-meta text-primary-60 ms-[0.5em]\">\n              <span>—Ryan Oksenhorn, Co-Founder, Zipline</span>\n             </figcaption>\n            </figure>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </section>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none not-first:mt-16\">\n     <div class=\"w-full toc-visible:md:grid-cols-9 gap-x-(--grid-gap) [--grid-gap:8px] md:[--grid-gap:16px] lg:[--grid-gap:24px] toc-content-heading scroll-mt-header-h\" id=\"set-spend-controls-around-the-way-teams-work\">\n      <div class=\"full-grid-content:@md:col-span-full full-grid-content:@md:col-start-1 col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none\">\n       <h2 class=\"text-h3 scroll-mt-header-h\"><span>Set spend controls around the way teams work</span></h2>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none not-first:mt-6\">\n     <p class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\"><span>Earlier this year, we introduced granular </span><a href=\"https://help.openai.com/en/articles/20001001-setting-usage-limits-for-custom-roles-in-chatgpt-enterprise\" class=\"transition ease-curve-a duration-250 text-primary-100 hover:text-primary-60 relative underline-offset-[0.25rem] decoration-1 underline\" target=\"_blank\"><span>credit usage limits</span>⁠<span class=\"sr-only\">(opens in a new window)</span></a><span> for custom roles in ChatGPT Enterprise, helping workspace owners manage advanced model usage across different types of users without one-size-fits-all restrictions.</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full group not-first:mt-16 not-last:mb-16\">\n     <figure class=\"w-full toc-visible:md:grid-cols-9 gap-x-(--grid-gap) [--grid-gap:8px] md:[--grid-gap:16px] lg:[--grid-gap:24px]\">\n      <div class=\"col-span-full flex min-h-0 flex-col gap-6 toc-visible:@md:col-span-8 toc-visible:@md:col-start-1\">\n       <div class=\"flex min-h-0 w-full min-w-0 flex-col gap-6 @sm:flex-row items-center\">\n        <div class=\"w-full mx-auto ease-curve-c duration-medium transition-opacity max-w-container-desktop relative min-h-0\">\n         <div class=\"relative min-h-0 w-full\">\n          <div class=\"size-full\">\n           <div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-md aspect-auto size-full bg-surface-loading\">\n            <img alt=\"End-user view of spend controls and requesting limit increase\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"mx-auto\" style=\"color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1728px) 1728px, 100vw\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260618192256_End-user_view_of_spend_controls_and_requesting_limit_increase.png 640w, https://image.jido.dev/20260618192256_End-user_view_of_spend_controls_and_requesting_limit_increase.png 750w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/edace8b1-1666-4494-7d1e-2db4e4be4600/public 828w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/712d9424-ebeb-4aef-dd9b-b27a6bfd2e00/public 1080w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bf9aae2f-a92d-4aad-6cc0-e01895864200/public 1200w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/afa91934-9b73-4fa1-d138-1eae087a4800/public 1920w, https://image.jido.dev/20260618192256_End-user_view_of_spend_controls_and_requesting_limit_increase.png 2048w, https://image.jido.dev/20260618192256_End-user_view_of_spend_controls_and_requesting_limit_increase.png 3840w\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260618192256_End-user_view_of_spend_controls_and_requesting_limit_increase.png\">\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <figcaption class=\"text-caption col-span-full flex w-full flex-col items-center gap-3\">\n        <div class=\"relative mt-3 w-full text-center\">\n         <div class=\"flex w-full items-end justify-between\">\n          <div class=\"grow\">\n           <div class=\"text-caption text-copy-secondary text-pretty\">\n            <div class=\"[&amp;&gt;p]:text-caption prose [&amp;&gt;p]:text-primary-100 my-0! max-w-none [&amp;&gt;p]:my-0\">\n             <p class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\"><i><span>End-user view of spend controls and requesting limit increase.</span></i></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </figcaption>\n      </div>\n     </figure>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none not-first:mt-6\">\n     <p class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\"><span>Now admins can also set a default limit for their ChatGPT Enterprise workspace, configure limits for specific groups, and create individual overrides for people who need more capacity. Employees can see their credit usage against their available budget, request additional credits when needed, and include context about what they’re working on so admins can make an informed decision. This allows individual power users to keep working without interruption or the need to increase limits for everyone else.</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none not-first:mt-6\">\n     <p class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\"><span>Together, these updated controls help companies deploy intelligence more thoughtfully at scale, while giving teams the capabilities they need to do high-impact work.</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none not-first:mt-16\">\n     <div class=\"w-full toc-visible:md:grid-cols-9 gap-x-(--grid-gap) [--grid-gap:8px] md:[--grid-gap:16px] lg:[--grid-gap:24px] toc-content-heading scroll-mt-header-h\" id=\"availability-and-what-you-can-do-next\">\n      <div class=\"full-grid-content:@md:col-span-full full-grid-content:@md:col-start-1 col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none\">\n       <h2 class=\"text-h3 scroll-mt-header-h\"><span>Availability and what you can do next</span></h2>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none not-first:mt-6\">\n     <p class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\"><span>ChatGPT Enterprise admins can start using the new analytics and updated spend controls today. Users in these workspaces can also view their credit usage by going to their workspace settings.</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none not-first:mt-6\">\n     <p class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\"><span>Learn more in the help center on </span><a href=\"https://help.openai.com/articles/20001001\" class=\"transition ease-curve-a duration-250 text-primary-100 hover:text-primary-60 relative underline-offset-[0.25rem] decoration-1 underline\" target=\"_blank\"><span>usage limits</span>⁠<span class=\"sr-only\">(opens in a new window)</span></a><span> and the </span><a href=\"https://help.openai.com/articles/12289294\" class=\"transition ease-curve-a duration-250 text-primary-100 hover:text-primary-60 relative underline-offset-[0.25rem] decoration-1 underline\" target=\"_blank\"><span>global admin console</span>⁠<span class=\"sr-only\">(opens in a new window)</span></a><span>.</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-span-full toc-visible:@md:col-start-2 max-w-none not-first:mt-6\">\n     <p class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\"><span>Have questions about how best to implement controls for your workspace? Contact us </span><a class=\"transition ease-curve-a duration-250 text-primary-100 hover:text-primary-60 relative underline-offset-[0.25rem] decoration-1 underline\" href=\"https://openai.com/contact-sales/\"><span>here</span></a><span>, or reach out directly to your OpenAI team.</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"w-full\">\n   <div class=\"flex w-auto\">\n    <div class=\"w-full no-scrollbar overflow-x-auto overflow-y-hidden\">\n     <div class=\"flex min-w-224 px-6 pe-6 flex-none\">\n      <div class=\"relative mb-8 ps-6 min-w-[calc(100%/3)] ps-0 last:me-0\"></div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "OpenAI 为 ChatGPT Enterprise 推出了新的信用用量分析与更新版支出控制功能，让管理员能够精细洞察 AI 使用情况，并灵活管理成本。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "OpenAI 为 ChatGPT Enterprise 推出了新的信用用量分析与更新版支出控制功能，让管理员能够精细洞察 AI 使用情况，并灵活管理成本。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了 ChatGPT Enterprise 的新功能：全局管理控制台中的信用用量分析以及更新版的支出控制。分析功能提供了 ChatGPT 和 Codex 信用消耗的统一视图，使管理员能够追踪趋势、识别高频用户，并按用户、产品和模型细分支出。数据还可通过统一的 Cost API 获取。更新后的支出控制功能允许管理员设置默认工作区限制、配置特定群组限制以及创建个人覆盖额度。员工可以查看自己的预算使用情况，并在有需要时申请额外信用额度。文章还包含了早期采用者 Zipline 的推荐语，并附有帮助中心文档链接。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "新的信用用量分析功能提供了跨用户、产品和模型的 AI 消耗精细视图。",
      "explanation": "全局管理控制台统一了 ChatGPT 和 Codex 的信用数据，使管理员能够追踪趋势、识别高频用户，并分析支出模式，以区分高价值使用与异常情况。"
    },
    {
      "point": "更新后的支出控制功能提供了灵活的多层级成本管理。",
      "explanation": "管理员可以设置默认工作区限制、特定群组限制以及个人覆盖额度。员工可以在有需要时申请额外信用额度，让高频用户在不全面提升限制的情况下无中断工作。"
    },
    {
      "point": "分析数据可通过统一的 Cost API 获取，用于更深入的定制分析。",
      "explanation": "企业可以将信用用量数据集成到自有系统中，以实现更复杂的报告和成本优化工作流程。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "这些新工具正在帮助我们更快地提升员工生产力，同时保持安全防护措施到位。",
    "凭借更清晰的可见性和更灵活的控制，组织可以主动管理成本，为团队提供所需的访问权限，并确保 AI 投资集中在最重要的工作上。"
  ],
